  <sharedSelectionEntries>
    <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Battle Traits: Allies of the Free Cities" hidden="false" id="c56a-04ea-59ee-567b" publicationId="a746-732d-1a22-460">
      <profiles>
        <profile name="Forces of Order" typeId="907f-a48-6a04-f788" typeName="Ability (Passive)" hidden="false" id="7f17-ebfc-446e-4d8e">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="b977-7c5e-33b2-428e"/>
            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="fd7f-888d-3257-a12b">While 3 friendly **^^Allies of the Free Cities^^** units are wholly within 12&quot; of each other and 1 of those units has the **^^Aelf^^** keyword, 1 of those units has the **^^Duardin^^** keyword, and 1 of those units has the **^^Sigmarite^^** keyword:
• Those units have **^^Ward (5+)^^** against shooting attacks.
• Add 3 to those units&apos; control scores.
• Add 1 to wound rolls for those units&apos; combat attacks.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
          <attributes>
            <attribute name="Color" typeId="50fe-4f29-6bc3-dcc6">Black</attribute>
            <attribute name="Type" typeId="bf11-4e10-3ab1-06f4">Special</attribute>
            <attribute name="Parent Node" typeId="e2e1-15ca-d345-22b8"/>
          </attributes>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Form Up, Allies!" typeId="59b6-d47a-a68a-5dcc" typeName="Ability (Activated)" hidden="false" id="ef51-6de3-f104-3713">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Timing" typeId="652c-3d84-4e7-14f4">Start of Battle Round</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="bad3-f9c5-ba46-18cb">Pick a friendly **^^Allies of the Free Cities^^** unit to use this ability, then pick 2 other visible friendly **^^Allies of the Free Cities^^** units wholly within 12&quot; of it to be the targets.
The unit using this ability and the targets:
• cannot be **under orders**
• must each be a different unit type.</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="b6f1-ba36-6cd-3b03">For the rest of the battle round, the unit using this ability and the targets are **under orders**.
**Designer&apos;s Note:** *&apos;Unit type&apos; refers to the name of the warscroll (Core Rules, 4.0), e.g. &apos;Freeguild Cavalier-Marshal&apos; or &apos;Allies of the Free Cities Auric Hearthguard&apos;.*</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="12e8-3214-7d8f-1d0f"/>
            <characteristic name="Used By" typeId="1b32-c9d6-3106-166b"/>
          </characteristics>
          <attributes>
            <attribute name="Color" typeId="5a11-eab3-180c-ddf5">Black</attribute>
            <attribute name="Type" typeId="6d16-c86b-2698-85a4">Special</attribute>
            <attribute name="Parent Node" typeId="2d74-4dcd-8468-87fa"/>
          </attributes>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
      <categoryLinks>
        <categoryLink name="Reference" hidden="false" id="2f2a-76ea-59aa-b756" targetId="3360-1158-e879-9606" primary="true"/>
      </categoryLinks>
    </selectionEntry>
    <selectionEntry type="unit" import="true" name="Allies of the Free Cities Auric Hearthguard" hidden="false" id="cb43-04f6-95c8-f576" publicationId="a746-732d-1a22-460">
      <profiles>
        <profile name="Auric Hearthguard" typeId="ff03-376e-972f-8ab2" typeName="Unit" hidden="false" id="96cc-8318-c739-eb36">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Move" typeId="fed0-d1b3-1bb8-c501">4&quot;</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Health" typeId="96be-54ae-ce7b-10b7">2</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Save" typeId="1981-ef09-96f6-7aa9">6+</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Control" typeId="6c6f-8510-9ce1-fc6e">1</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Lava-encrusted" typeId="907f-a48-6a04-f788" typeName="Ability (Passive)" hidden="false" id="cc23-74af-4d76-a458">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="b977-7c5e-33b2-428e"/>
            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="fd7f-888d-3257-a12b">While this unit is **under orders**, each time a shooting attack made by this unit scores a critical hit, subtract 1&quot; from the target unit’s Move characteristic until the start of your next turn (this effect is cumulative). This ability cannot reduce the target unit’s unmodified Move characteristic below half its starting value.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
          <attributes>
            <attribute name="Color" typeId="50fe-4f29-6bc3-dcc6">Blue</attribute>
            <attribute name="Type" typeId="bf11-4e10-3ab1-06f4">Movement</attribute>
            <attribute name="Parent Node" typeId="e2e1-15ca-d345-22b8"/>
          </attributes>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
      <categoryLinks>
        <categoryLink name="INFANTRY" hidden="false" id="a992-c379-70ed-e1b9" targetId="75d6-6995-dfcc-3898" primary="true"/>
        <categoryLink name="CHAMPION" hidden="false" id="4fab-bd86-f379-2768" targetId="f679-3bcb-d664-9ac3" primary="false"/>
        <categoryLink name="ORDER" hidden="false" id="b68d-38a8-8d16-357b" targetId="ee22-3575-6590-25c" primary="false"/>
        <categoryLink name="WARD (6+)" hidden="false" id="3cc2-0eaa-2161-342b" targetId="70a4-383f-421f-52cd" primary="false"/>
        <categoryLink name="DUARDIN" hidden="false" id="2f58-f369-427f-a8be" targetId="72e3-7b1b-cb94-4cbd" primary="false"/>
        <categoryLink name="MUSICIAN (1/10)" hidden="false" id="f7f0-bf30-86a8-3527" targetId="eeed-ef77-b0d-fa9d" primary="false"/>
        <categoryLink name="CITIES OF SIGMAR" hidden="false" id="5282-096e-3b17-8393" targetId="4999-8ae2-e1bb-ba5" primary="false"/>
        <categoryLink name="ALLIES OF THE FREE CITIES" hidden="false" id="2f5c-597b-381e-a6ac" targetId="1d86-e6a8-bb97-b2b9" primary="false"/>
      </categoryLinks>
